Van Persie on Emery: &ldquo;What is his philosophy? He&rsquo;s changing a lot, he&rsquo;s changing tactics a lot. It looks to me he&rsquo;s changing his playing style based on the opponent. You need to form a basis from your own strengths.&rdquo; [BT]<br />
<br />
Robin Van Persie on Arsenal: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s difficult to say because if you look at the teams under Wenger, Wenger&rsquo;s teams always used to play from his philosophy. You see the same happening with Klopp &amp; Guardiola at Liverpool &amp; Man City, but with Emery I don&rsquo;t really see his philosophy.&rdquo;

